room_title: Escape room "Mine Trap" by Escape Room Park City in Salt Lake City
room_description: Enjoy a piece of Park City's past with fun mine tour. Relive the days of old... oh wait a minute, something is happening! The mine has caved in! All exits have been blocked! You have an hour of air to find your way out of the mine. Can you and your group using just your wits, imagination and powers of deduction beat the room, in just an hour?
